sources.description:
4K RESTORATION! Complete 13-chapter Cliffhanger!
Starring: Kent Taylor, Ralph Morgan, Irene Hervey, Robert Armstrong
Directed by: Ray Taylor & Noel M. Smith

Over a sinister radio broadcast, a self-possessed master criminal declares his "The League of Murdered Men" will exact revenge upon the city unless all officials are kicked out of office. A hard-driving police detective must end this reign of terror and uncover how the madman's "League"  can be composed of public enemies who have all been officially proclaimed dead!
